I am doing enough and I am enough. Thank you! <3

Yoga is the first type of fitness where I arrive with no expectations. In every other fitness, running, HIIT, circuits I always expect to be better than last time and get annoyed if I can’t run faster, lift more, do more reps. With yoga I focus on how I feel today, if it’s a good day, then great. If it’s a hard day, then fine, that’s why they call it ‘practice’. I only expect that I will learn. Thank you Adrienne
